strength; kR^ita nishchayaH = is firmly determined; tva arthe = in your cause.

24. tau nR^isimhau = those two lions among men; Rama and sakaasham too;
mahaasattvau = of great strength; mama pR^iSTha gatau = sitting on my shoulders;
aagamiSyataH = can come; tvat sakaasham = to you; uditau chandra suuryaav iva 
= like the rising sun and the moon.

27. shroSyasi = you will hear; achiraat = within a short time;
svanam = the sound; kapi mukhyanaam = of the excellent of monkeys; nardataam 
= resonating; laN^kaa malaya saanuSu = on the mountain-peaks of Mount Malayaa in Lanka; 
shail ambudan nikaashaanaam = like mountains and clouds.
